title: Storacell by Powerpax SlimLine AA Battery Storage Container - Holds 4 Batteries, Orange (Pack of 1)
features: Store your batteries in a compact, easy to find caddy; holds 4 AA batteries

Terminal protection at both ends regardless of how the battery is inserted
